      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "# Student Success Prediction & Retention Strategy\n",
        "\n",
        "## Overview\n",
        "In this project, I analyzed student engagement and performance data to understand the key factors that influence course completion in an online learning environment.\n",
        "\n",
        "The goal is to identify students at risk of dropping out early and provide actionable insights that can help improve retention."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "L2sBq3VOWGMr"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "\n",
        "from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\n",
        "from sklearn.compose import ColumnTransformer\n",
        "from sklearn.preprocessing import OneHotEncoder, StandardScaler\n",
        "from sklearn.pipeline import Pipeline\n",
        "from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression\n",
        "from sklearn.metrics import classification_report, confusion_matrix, accuracy_score\n",
        "\n",
        "# Load data\n",
        "path = '/content/online_course_engagement_data.csv'\n",
        "df = pd.read_csv(path)\n",
        "\n",
        "df.head()"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "2SQLrpSVWwv2"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
